# Lux CRM Agent Instructions (Template)

Use this file as the primary implementation contract for the CRM agent.

## Core requirements
- FastAPI backend for ingestion, scoring, drafting, and resolution APIs
- Neo4j Aura for context graph
- Neon Postgres + pgvector for interaction chunks and embeddings
- n8n workflows for ingestion triggers and scheduled jobs
- Next.js UI for priority list, contact detail, news matching, drafts, and resolution

## Non-negotiables
- Every claim must have provenance pointers to evidence
- Sensitive facts are excluded from drafts by default
- Contradictions must create resolution tasks

